The document describes the wiring used which corresponds to the code.

The accelerometer module has 5 pins, namely
  GND - To be connected to Arduino's GND
  VCC - To be connected to Arduino's 5V
  X - To be connected to Analog Pin A3
  Y - To be connected to Analog Pin A2
  Z - To be connected to Analog Pin A1

The 16x2 LCD is I2C:
  GND - To be connected to Arduino's GND
  VCC - To be connected to Arduino's 5V
  SDA - To be connected to Analog Pin A4
  SLC - To be connected to Analog Pin A5




